text: Alfina Sukhanova (born 1 January 1944) is a Soviet alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of the Soviet Union Category:Alpine skiers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Novosibirsk
